message.entry: Cannot evaluate LWM transformation at some output locations which are beyond the RadiiOfInfluence of control point polynomials. Try spreading control points more uniformly over image.
LWMTData must be a 6-by-2-by-M double matrix.
LWMTData must not contain NaN or Inf.
ControlPoints must be an M-by-2 double matrix.
ControlPoints must not contain NaN or Inf.
RadiiOfInfluence must be an M-by-1 double matrix.
RadiiOfInfluence must not contain NaN or Inf.
RadiiOfInfluence must contain only positive numbers.
